<h2>Business outline</h2>

<ol class="m00"> 
<li>Cloud Computing Business<br />
Service of Cloud computing solution (Package-type, Resource On-Demand, etc.) based on Network business and Data Center Business</li>
<li>Network Business<br />
Construction of a variety of network system (Internet, VPN, etc.) and supply of associated networking equipment</li>
<li>Data Center Business<br />
A variety of services based on Server Business</li>
</ol>

